snippet.title: Australian Minister Makes Fun of Depp Apology
snippet.description:
An Australian politician on Tuesday poked fun at the video recorded by actor Johnny Depp and his wife Amber Heard over their now infamous dog smuggling spat with Australian quarantine officials. (April 19)
